rows.label: tev910101_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev910101_SEL0020
rows.name: Ask how her work is going.

rows.label: tev910101_MSG0030
rows.name:
Another thing us Prospectors do
besides gathering resources is log new
discoveries in our databases.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910101_MSG0040
rows.name:
The resources we had on Earth don't
necessarily occur on this planet. We often
have to recreate them from scratch.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910101_MSG0050
rows.name:
If you ever come across something new,
make note of where you found it. Never
know when you'll need a couple more![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910101_JNK0060
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev910101_SEL0070
rows.name: Ask how she's been doing lately.

rows.label: tev910101_MSG0080
rows.name:
We're pretty darn lucky we
managed to crash on a planet
that's so similar to Earth.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910101_MSG0090
rows.name:
Already the very first surveys showed us it
had minerals, plants, and fauna analogous
to livestock. Plenty to get started with![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910101_MSG0100
rows.name:
Working hand-in-glove with the
Interceptors should let us secure bigger
and better sources. I'm hopeful![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910101_JNK0110
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev910101_SEL0120
rows.name: Ask how Omomo's doing.

rows.label: tev910101_MSG0130
rows.name:
You don't have to worry about her.
I promise to support her and make sure
she can live her days out peacefully.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910101_MSG0140
rows.name:
She's in a much better mood than before.
I really think she made the right choice by
joining us here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910101_MSG0150
rows.name:
Thank you so much for convincing her.
It really... It really means a lot.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910101_JNK0160
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev910101_SEL0170
rows.name: Ask about her feelings regarding Nopon.

rows.label: tev910101_MSG0180
rows.name:
At first, I thought they were, uh...
How shall I put it? A real...happy-go-lucky
species, let's say.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910101_MSG0190
rows.name:
But after meeting Omomo in Sylvalum,
I realized it was narrow-minded of me
to think that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910101_MSG0200
rows.name:
Nopon forge strong bonds with others,
just like we do. Omomo's no different...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910101_MSG0210
rows.name:
She's in Sylvalum, living on the
Delusians North Summit.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910101_MSG0220
rows.name:
She's a precious, precious friend to me.
Please...do what you can for her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910101_MSG0230
rows.name: Cancel

rows.label: tev910101_MSG0240
rows.name: Cancel
